OL,3,CPub owners to pay #285K after woman
OL,4,Cdied from falling down cellar stairs
OL,6,FThe owners of a pub where a customer
OL,7,Fdied after falling through an unlocked
OL,8,Fcellar door has been ordered to pay a
OL,9,Ffine and costs totalling more than
OL,10,F#285,000.
OL,12,FJulie Hyatt, 57, was having lunch with
OL,13,Fher husband, Paul, and friends at The
OL,14,FLangton Arms at Church Langton, near
OL,15,FMarket Harborough, in Leicestershire,
OL,16,Fin May 2023.
