OL,3,CPub owners to pay #285K after woman
OL,4,Cdied from falling down cellar stairs
OL,6,FShe hadn't been drinking and was
OL,7,Ffollowing signs to the toilet, when
OL,8,Fshe opened an unmarked and unlocked
OL,9,Fdoor, not knowing it was to the pub's
OL,10,Fcellar, and fell down a steep flight
OL,11,Fof stairs.
OL,13,FMrs Hyatt suffered serious injuries
OL,14,Ffrom which she died in hospital 12
OL,15,Fdays later.
