OL,3,CPub owners to pay #285K after woman
OL,4,Cdied from falling down cellar stairs
OL,6,FAt Leicester Magistrates' Court, the
OL,7,FRedCat Pub Company, based in London,
OL,8,Fadmitted breaching the Health and
OL,9,FSafety at Work Act by exposing persons
OL,10,Fnot in its employment to a risk to
OL,11,Ftheir health and safety.
OL,13,FAt the hearing, held on the second
OL,14,Fanniversary of Mrs Hyatt's funeral,
OL,15,Fthe company was fined #240,000 and
OL,16,Fordered to pay costs of #43,633.06p
OL,17,Falong with a #2,000 surcharge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
