OL,3,CPub owners to pay #285K after woman
OL,4,Cdied from falling down cellar stairs
OL,6,FIn determining the level of fine and
OL,7,Fcosts, District Judge Nick Watson said
OL,8,Fhe had taken into account that
OL,9,FRedCat's parent company had a turnover
OL,10,Fof more than #120million.
OL,12,FHe said he wanted to "bring it home to
OL,13,Fshareholders and management that they
OL,14,Fmust take health and safety seriously".
OL,16,FHe added "Any sentence that I impose
OL,17,Fcould not equate to the loss of Mrs
OL,18,FHyatt to her family and friends."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
