OL,6,FIn statements read to the court, it
OL,7,Fwas revealed Mrs Hyatt and her husband
OL,8,Fhad been looking forward to retirement
OL,9,Fand moving to the Norfolk coast.
OL,11,FMarried since 1987, they shared many
OL,12,Finterests and a passion for sport with
OL,13,FMrs Hyatt being a Leicester City
OL,14,Fseason ticket holder for more than 30
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FThe court heard that Mrs Hyatt's death
OL,18,Fwas foreseeable. The company had
OL,19,Ffailed to properly train staff and had
OL,20,Fleft customers confused by inadequate
OL,21,Fand inconsistent signs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
