OL,3,CPub owners to pay #285K after woman
OL,4,Cdied from falling down cellar stairs
OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court,
OL,7,FRichard Lewis, CEO of RedCat Pub
OL,8,FCompany, expressed his "sincere
OL,9,Fpersonal regret" as the death was
OL,10,F"entirely avoidable". The company said
OL,11,Fit accepted full responsibility.
OL,13,F"We are genuinely very sorry ... We
OL,14,Fhave plainly failed the Hyatt family.
OL,15,FWe will do all we can to prevent
OL,16,Fanything of the like happening again,"
OL,17,Fadded Mr Lewis.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
