OL,6,FThe court heard the company had since
OL,7,Fput in place risk assessments and
OL,8,Fevaluated the way in which it conducts
OL,9,Fstaff training in relation to health
OL,10,Fand safety.
OL,12,FITV News Central Correspondent Peter
OL,13,FBearne sat down with the Paul Hyatt
OL,14,Flast year, who is still waiting for
OL,15,Fanswers more than 12 months after his
OL,16,Fwife's death.
OL,18,FIn the time that passed, Paul, from
OL,19,FCountesthorpe, repeatedly contacted
OL,20,Fthe council for updates on the case,
OL,21,Fbut said he has got nowhere.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
