OL,6,FPaul has learned Harborough District
OL,7,FCouncil have brought in a solicitor
OL,8,Ffrom another council to help with the
OL,9,Fcase.
OL,11,FIn 2024, the council asked Paul for
OL,12,FJulie's death certificate, something
OL,13,Fthat the family won't get until after
OL,14,Fthe inquest.
OL,16,FITV News Central is also aware of two
OL,17,Fother similar cases elsewhere in the
OL,18,Fcountry which came to court in 12
OL,19,Fmonths.
