OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central,
OL,7,Ffollowing the incident, Paul said: "It
OL,8,Fwas hell at the time. I was in some
OL,9,Fvery, very dark places."
OL,11,FHe added: "I just wish somebody would
OL,12,Fgo in and shake that department up and
OL,13,Fget this sorted. Enough is enough. All
OL,14,FI want is justice...I lost my wife."
OL,16,FIn response, Harborough District
OL,17,FCouncil say that they sympathise with
OL,18,FMr Hyatt's frustrations.
