OL,6,FThey told ITV News Central this case
OL,7,Fis a complex and lengthy criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation, and they're unable to
OL,9,Fcomment on its progress.
OL,11,F"Specialist legal resource, they
OL,12,Fadded, was allocated without delay.
OL,13,FThey said they've liaised with Mr
OL,14,FHyatt and his solicitor as much as
OL,15,Fthey can, but there's a limit to what
OL,16,Fthey can disclose."
